<p>If you're wondering, the song at the top is from the film Her and it's called <em>The Moon Song</em> by Karen O, you can find the link to the original song <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SU6KFnGF9M8">here</a>. Most of the coding was <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">stolen</span> borrowed from people like Randomini and others, I created the banners myself using images from /wg/ on 4chan. I would add author commentary for every article but I wanted this page to be short, simple, sum up my personality, and look aesthetically pleasing.</p>
<p><sub><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> The image for &quot;Scarf&quot; was taken from the animated short <em>Paperman</em>. The image was digitally edited by me and I claim no ownership over the original image.</sub></p>

